{
  "texts": [
    "The framework can inform academic research and guide practical interventions, bridging the knowledgepractice gap.",
    "The convergence of AI and cyberattacks therefore presents new challenges and opportunities for cybersecurity.",
    "As AI-driven threats evolve, so we must evolve our understanding, strategies, and frameworks.",
    "This paper underscores the need for collaborative, interdisciplinary efforts to address these challenges and seize the opportunities.",
    "The AICD Framework serves as a beacon for future research and interventions."
  ]
}